column1: Data Provider                    : DMC Dirección Meteorológica de Chile, GAW Program (https://woudc.org/)
Data Compilation                 : 05 April, 2021, by CR2 Center for Climate and Resilience Research. Linearly interpolated data every 100 m
Variables measured by sonde      : Geopotential Height, Pressure, Ozone Partial Pressure, Temperature, Relative Humidity, Wind Speed, Wind Direction
Variables calculated from data   : Mixing Ratio Ozone by volume, Column Ozone, Zonal and Meridional Winds, Potential Temperature, Equivalent Potential Temperature, Water Vapor Mixing Ratio by mass
